<translate>
<!--T:1-->
'''VRCat''' is the official mascot of [[<tvar name="1">Special:MyLanguage/VRChat</tvar>|VRChat]], a spacefaring orange cat with white markings. He wears a box on his head, with the [[<tvar name="2">Special:MyLanguage/VRC+</tvar>]] symbol on the side.

<!--T:2-->
== Appearances ==
VRCat's first appearance was [<tvar name="3">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=z-MKanCkDck</tvar> Introducing VRChat Plus] and has been seen in numerous official VRChat announcements and social media posts since.

<!--T:3-->
VRCat appears as the Early Supporter [[<tvar name="4">Special:MyLanguage/Badges</tvar>|Badge]] for users who bought [[<tvar name="5">Special:MyLanguage/VRC+</tvar>]] when it was first released. The badge can be pet on a user's profile on the website.

<!--T:4-->
After purchasing VRC+, VRCat will appear on the user's [[<tvar name="6">Special:MyLanguage/Quick Menu</tvar>]]. Clicking VRCat in this menu multiple times will cause dialogue to appear.<!-- any misspellings or grammatical errors in the dialogue table below are how they are displayed in-game -->
